title: GOP Makes Fresh Effort to End Federal Funding for Planned Parenthood
text: House Speaker Paul Ryan (R., Wis.) said on Thursday that Republicans will once more attempt to strip Planned Parenthood of its federal funding as part of their bill to repeal the Affordable Care Act.
